c i a test the cia had an opening for an assassin after all the background checks interviews and tests were done there were finalists men and a woman for the final test the cia agents took one of the men to a large metal door and handed him a gun we must know that you will follow your instructions no matter what the circumstances inside this room you will find your wife sitting in a chair kill her the man said you can't be serious i could never shoot my wife the agent said then you're not the right man for this job take your wife and go home the second man was given the same instructions he took the gun and went into the room all was quiet for about five minutes then the man came out with tears in his eyes i tried but i can't kill my wife the agent said you don't have what it takes take your wife and go home finally it was the woman's turn she was given the same instructions to kill her husband she took the gun and went into the room shots were heard one shot after another eight in a row they heard screaming crashing and banging on the walls after a few minutes all was quiet the door opened slowly and there stood the woman she wiped the sweat from her brow this gun is loaded with blanks she said i had to beat him to death with the chair moral never put a woman to the test good one i laughed so hard i farted just a little bit John F. Kennedy assassination Shaggy dog story Sin City The Inside The Shining (film) Syphon Filter Max Payne Blood Simple Episodes of Lost (Season 1) StarCraft: Uprising Jam (TV series) Cube (film) Vegeta United Airlines Flight 93 Oplan Bojinka Mumia Abu-Jamal Plame affair Doom enemies The Curse of Fenric Kill Bill Combine (Half-Life 2) Rais massacre Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Reservoir Dogs Detailed timeline of the assassination of John F. Kennedy The Dalek Invasion of Earth The Midnight Sun Trapped in the Closet Donald Neilson The Big Goodbye (TNG episode) Dutch Schultz Richard Chase Internal ballistics Terminal ballistics 